Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper focuses on attention models for vision and language tasks, specifically the Visual Dialog task. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with attention models for images and their integration with language models. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new method for attention in multimodal tasks, which is relevant to AI research. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new method for attention in machine learning models. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with attention models for text, which is relevant to information retrieval tasks.
